    

    Implement the game its name is sudoku 


    Task requirments

    a. game will have three different option
       1. EASY
       2. MEDIUM
       3. HARD

    b. Save the every play of game like record.
    c. user could easily replay the game from that record which they want.
    d. there are only three mistake (optional).
    e. suport the undo option like player ca use undo to go back their move.
    f. it will also support the redo option.
    g. time will also matter in the game(optional).
    h. if u want to take a high grade 80+ then your game have different size 9*9 3*3 etc.
    i. player also know about their number means how many number left to finish the borad.